comments: Duren (DET) steps forward and marginal body contact occurs with Sengun (HOU) as he receives the pass in the post.
Duren (DET) initiates contact to Sengun's (HOU) left arm, affecting his SQBR during the shot attempt in the post.
Green (HOU) is moving alongside Ivey's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Smith Jr. (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball during Ivey's (DET) driving shot attempt.  Any ensuing contact is incidental.
Livers (DET) reaches in and initiates contact with Martin Jr.'s (HOU) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Duren (DET) brings his off-arm toward Sengun (HOU) and marginal contact occurs as he hands the ball off.
Sengun (HOU) reaches in and initiates contact to Bagley III (DET) that affects his SQBR before he makes contact with the ball.
Joseph (DET) moves alongside Porter Jr. (HOU) and marginal two hand contact occurs as they engage off ball.
Porter Jr. (HOU) is slightly late to establish himself in Ivey's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs as the pick is set.
Ivey (DET) dislodges Green (HOU) from his defensive position during the drive to the basket.
Joseph (DET) moves alongside Green's (HOU) path and marginal body contact occurs as they engage during the driving shot attempt.
Ivey (DET) slightly extends his right leg outward and marginal contact occurs with Green (HOU) as he legally contests during the jump shot attempt.
Joseph (DET) commits a take foul on Sengun (HOU).
Sengun (HOU) jumps into Duren's (DET) body and initiates contact that affects his SQBR as he receives the pass.
Duren (DET) commits a take foul on Sengun (HOU).
